The paper proposes a framework for deep learning on hypergraphs, which is a topic that falls under the umbrella of machine learning and artificial intelligence. Specifically, the paper focuses on classification and regression tasks, which are common in the subfield of machine learning known as deep learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.SI (Social and Information Networks), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), and cs.CV (Computer Vision).
